  <div class="sec-sub" data-i18n="before_after_subtitle">Rezultatele reale ale clientelor noastre</div>
  <div class="grid3">
    <div class="ba-card"><div class="ba-imgs"><div class="ba-img ba-before" style="background-size:cover;background-image:url('img/healthy-food.jpg');position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;bottom:8px;left:8px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);color:white;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500">Înainte</span></div><div class="ba-img ba-after" style="background-size:cover;background-image:url('img/gallery-4.jpg');position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;bottom:8px;left:8px;background:rgba(91,138,114,0.8);color:white;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500">După</span></div></div><div class="ba-info"><div class="ba-name" data-i18n="ba_1_name">Ana, 34 ani</div><div class="ba-res" data-i18n="ba_1_res">−14 kg · −18 cm talie</div><div class="ba-time" data-i18n="ba_1_time">Durată: 4 luni</div></div></div>
    <div class="ba-card"><div class="ba-imgs"><div class="ba-img ba-before" style="background-size:cover;background-image:url('img/dumbbells.jpg');position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;bottom:8px;left:8px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);color:white;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500">Înainte</span></div><div class="ba-img ba-after" style="background-size:cover;background-image:url('img/gallery-5.jpg');position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;bottom:8px;left:8px;background:rgba(91,138,114,0.8);color:white;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500">După</span></div></div><div class="ba-info"><div class="ba-name" data-i18n="ba_2_name">Natalia, 28 ani</div><div class="ba-res" data-i18n="ba_2_res">−9 kg · tonus muscular</div><div class="ba-time" data-i18n="ba_2_time">Durată: 2 luni</div></div></div>
    <div class="ba-card"><div class="ba-imgs"><div class="ba-img ba-before" style="background-size:cover;background-image:url('img/planck-girls.jpg');position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;bottom:8px;left:8px;background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6);color:white;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500">Înainte</span></div><div class="ba-img ba-after" style="background-size:cover;background-image:url('img/gallery-6.jpg');position:relative;"><span style="position:absolute;bottom:8px;left:8px;background:rgba(91,138,114,0.8);color:white;padding:4px 8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500">După</span></div></div><div class="ba-info"><div class="ba-name" data-i18n="ba_3_name">Irina, 42 ani</div><div class="ba-res" data-i18n="ba_3_res">−11 kg · energie crescută</div><div class="ba-time" data-i18n="ba_3_time">Durată: 3 luni</div></div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider" id="booking" data-i18n="divider_booking">Programare</div>
<section class="sec sec-alt">
  <div class="sec-title" data-i18n="booking_title">Programează o ședință</div>
  <div class="sec-sub" data-i18n="booking_subtitle">Alege data și ora potrivite pentru tine</div>
  <div class="booking-wrap">
    <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:6px;font-weight:500">Selectează data:</div>
    <div class="slots-grid" id="slotsGrid"></div>
    <div id="timePicker" style="display:none;margin-top:14px">
      <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:8px;font-weight:500">Selectează ora:</div>
      <div id="timePills" style="display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap"></div>
    </div>
    <div id="bookForm" style="display:none;margin-top:20px">
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="fg"><label>Prenume</label><input id="bn" type="text" placeholder="Maria"></div>
        <div class="fg"><label>Telefon</label><input id="bp" type="tel" placeholder="+373 XX XXX XXX"></div>
      </div>
      <button class="btn-p" style="width:100%" onclick="confirmBook()">Confirmă programarea</button>
    </div>
    <div class="book-confirm" id="bookConf">
      <div style="font-weight:500;color:#3B6D11;margin-bottom:4px">Programare confirmată!</div>
      <div id="bookDetails" style="font-size:12px;color:#3B6D11;line-height:1.6"></div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:#639922;margin-top:6px">Te vom contacta pentru confirmare finală.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider" id="calc" data-i18n="divider_calc">Calculatoare</div>
<section class="sec">
  <div class="sec-title" data-i18n="calc_title">Calculatoare fitness</div>
  <div class="sec-sub" data-i18n="calc_subtitle">Formule reale BMR & TDEE</div>
  <div style="display:flex;justify-content:center">
    <div class="calc-tabs">
      <div class="ctab active" onclick="switchCalc('imc',this)">Calculator IMC</div>
      <div class="ctab" onclick="switchCalc('cal',this)">Calculator calorii</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-block active" id="calc-imc">
    <div class="form-row">
      <div class="fg"><label>Înălțime (cm)</label><input type="number" id="ih" value="165" min="140" max="200" oninput="calcIMC()"></div>
      <div class="fg"><label>Greutate (kg)</label><input type="number" id="iw" value="68" min="40" max="150" oninput="calcIMC()"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="calc-result">
      <div class="calc-val" id="imcVal">24.9</div>
      <div class="calc-label">Indicele de Masă Corporală</div>
      <div class="calc-interp" id="imcInterp" style="color:#3B6D11">Greutate normală</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px">Subponderal &lt;18.5 · Normal 18.5–24.9 · Supraponderal 25–29.9 · Obez ≥30</div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-p" style="width:100%;margin-top:14px" onclick="sc('contact')">Doresc un program personalizat</button>
  </div>
  <div class="calc-block" id="calc-cal">
    <div class="form-row">
      <div class="fg"><label>Vârstă (ani)</label><input type="number" id="ca" value="30" oninput="calcCal()"></div>
      <div class="fg"><label>Greutate (kg)</label><input type="number" id="cw" value="65" oninput="calcCal()"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-row">
      <div class="fg"><label>Înălțime (cm)</label><input type="number" id="ch" value="165" oninput="calcCal()"></div>
      <div class="fg"><label>Nivel activitate</label><select id="cact" onchange="calcCal()"><option value="1.2">Sedentar</option><option value="1.375" selected>Ușor activ (1–3/săpt)</option><option value="1.55">Moderat activ (3–5/săpt)</option><option value="1.725">Foarte activ (6–7/săpt)</option></select></div>
    </div>
    <div class="calc-result">
      <div class="calc-val" id="calVal">1985</div>
      <div class="calc-label">Calorii zilnice recomandate (TDEE)</div>
      <div class="calc-interp" style="color:#3B6D11">BMR: <span id="calBMR">1442</span> kcal</div>
      <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px">Slăbire: −300–500 kcal · Menținere: TDEE · Masă: +200–300 kcal</div>
    </div>
    <button class="btn-p" style="width:100%;margin-top:14px" onclick="sc('contact')">Vreau plan nutrițional</button>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="section-divider" id="quiz" data-i18n="divider_quiz">Quiz fitness</div>
<section class="sec sec-alt">
  <div class="sec-title" data-i18n="quiz_title">Quiz fitness</div>
  <div class="sec-sub" data-i18n="quiz_subtitle">5 întrebări — descoperă programul potrivit</div>
  <div class="quiz-prog"><div class="quiz-prog-bar" id="qbar" style="width:20%"></div></div>
  <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--color-text-secondary);margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center;max-width:480px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto" id="qctr">Întrebarea 1 din 5</div>
  <div class="quiz-step active" id="qs1">
    <div class="quiz-q">Care este obiectivul tău principal?</div>
    <div class="quiz-sub">Alege varianta care ți se potrivește cel mai bine.</div>
    <div class="quiz-opts">
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'goal','slabire')">Slăbire</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'goal','tonus')">Tonifiere</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'goal','masa')">Masă musculară</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'goal','sanatate')">Sănătate generală</div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-nav"><div></div><button class="qnext" onclick="goQ(2)">Continuă</button></div>
  </div>
  <div class="quiz-step" id="qs2">
    <div class="quiz-q">Câte antrenamente pe săptămână poți face?</div>
    <div class="quiz-sub">Fii realistă cu programul tău.</div>
    <div class="quiz-opts">
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'freq','1-2')">1–2 ori</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'freq','3-4')">3–4 ori</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'freq','5+')">5+ ori</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'freq','0')">Abia încep</div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-nav"><button class="qback" onclick="goQ(1)">Înapoi</button><button class="qnext" onclick="goQ(3)">Continuă</button></div>
  </div>
  <div class="quiz-step" id="qs3">
    <div class="quiz-q">Care este nivelul tău de fitness?</div>
    <div class="quiz-sub">Honest este cel mai bun răspuns.</div>
    <div class="quiz-opts">
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'level','incepator')">Începător</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'level','mediu')">Intermediar</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'level','avansat')">Avansat</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'level','necunoscut')">Nu știu</div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-nav"><button class="qback" onclick="goQ(2)">Înapoi</button><button class="qnext" onclick="goQ(4)">Continuă</button></div>
  </div>
  <div class="quiz-step" id="qs4">
    <div class="quiz-q">Ai restricții alimentare sau probleme de sănătate?</div>
    <div class="quiz-sub">Informațiile sunt confidențiale.</div>
    <div class="quiz-opts">
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'health','nu')">Nu, sunt sănătoasă</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'health','diabet')">Diabet / glicemie</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'health','articulatii')">Articulații / spate</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'health','altele')">Altele</div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-nav"><button class="qback" onclick="goQ(3)">Înapoi</button><button class="qnext" onclick="goQ(5)">Continuă</button></div>
  </div>
  <div class="quiz-step" id="qs5">
    <div class="quiz-q">Când vrei să începi?</div>
    <div class="quiz-sub">Suntem pregătiți pentru tine oricând.</div>
    <div class="quiz-opts">
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'start','imediat')">Imediat!</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'start','saptamana')">Săptămâna aceasta</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'start','luna')">Luna viitoare</div>
      <div class="qopt" onclick="selOpt(this,'start','analizez')">Mă mai gândesc</div>
    </div>
    <div class="quiz-nav"><button class="qback" onclick="goQ(4)">Înapoi</button><button class="qnext" onclick="finishQ()">Vezi rezultatul</button></div>
  </div>
  <div class="quiz-step" id="qs-r" style="max-width:540px;margin:0 auto">
    <div style="text-align:center;padding:16px 0">
      <div style="font-size:42px;margin-bottom:20px">🎯</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-accent);font-size:28px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:12px;color:var(--text)" id="qrtitle">Program recomandat</div>
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-body);font-size:16px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:28px;font-weight:400" id="qrtext"></div>

      <div id="specialist-card" style="background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.2);border-radius:20px;padding:0;margin-bottom:24px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:var(--shadow-lg)">
        <div style="height:240px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(16,185,129,0.1) 0%,rgba(16,185,129,0.08) 100%);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;overflow:hidden">
          <img id="specialist-photo" src="" alt="Specialist" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover">
        </div>
        <div style="padding:32px">
          <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:20px">
            <div style="font-family:var(--font-accent);font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:4px" id="specialist-name">Ana-Maria Ciobanu</div>
            <div style="font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;font-size:12px;color:var(--accent-primary);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:1px;text-transform:uppercase" id="specialist-role">Antrenor Certificat IFBB</div>
          </div>
          <div style="font-size:15px;color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;padding:16px 0;border-top:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.15);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.15)" id="specialist-desc">
            Specializare în antrenament pentru femei. 8+ ani experiență. Peste 200 cliente transformate.
          </div>
          <div style="margin-top:20px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px">
            <div style="text-align:center">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-accent);font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent-primary)">200+</div>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:4px">Clienți transformate</div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align:center">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-accent);font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:var(--accent-primary)">98%</div>
              <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:4px">Rate de satisfacție</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <button class="btn-p" style="width:100%;margin-top:20px" onclick="sc('contact')">Programează cu acest specialist</button>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="background:var(--bg-surface);border-radius:12px;padding:16px;font-size:12px;color:var(--text);margin-bottom:18px;line-height:1.6">
        <strong style="color:var(--text)">Ce urmează:</strong><br>
        Răspunsurile tale au fost salvate în CRM. Specialista te va contacta în 24h cu o propunere personalizată și va stabili prima ședință de probă.
      </div>

      <button class="btn-p" style="width:100%" onclick="sc('contact')">Înscrie-te acum</button>
      <button class="btn-s" style="width:100%;margin-top:8px" onclick="resetQ()">Reia quiz-ul</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

